para.verbatim:
Get a ModelField representing the request body for a path operation, combining all body parameters into a single field if necessary.
Used to check if it's form data (with `isinstance(body_field, params.Form)`) or JSON and to generate the JSON Schema for a request body.
This is **not** used to validate/parse the request body, that's done with each individual body parameter.
